      "author": "DavidSchenkler (David Schenkler | monday ambassador cohort 7)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>I just tried out monday vibe, and I have to say that I’m very impressed. There is definitely a lot of improvement and growth needed, but for its first stages it is really impressive.</p>\n<p>I created an app that creates a very extensive Column Dictionary. I can write descriptions, give descriptions per label in statuses, and even paste related automation URLs. This has been a severe need in our company to be used for various functions such as SOP and training, as well as tracking column use and requirement.</p>\n<p>The best part is that this app took 10 minutes to build! Insane!</p>\n<p>I think there is a lot of potential to <a class=\"hashtag-cooked\" href=\"/tag/monday_vibe\"><span class=\"hashtag-icon-placeholder\"></span><span>monday_vibe</span></a> , and I look forward to its continuing growth!</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/c/0/c057580c3c7ef8dbdaa7e180c9ae5dc0795783b5.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.15.03\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/c/0/c057580c3c7ef8dbdaa7e180c9ae5dc0795783b5_2_607x500.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.15.03\" width=\"607\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.15.03</span><span class=\"informations\">791×651 61.3 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/1/9/1999a65cdbcbcb96e61ec1bceec72e086bcb0ba9.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.16.53\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/1/9/1999a65cdbcbcb96e61ec1bceec72e086bcb0ba9_2_690x338.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.16.53\" width=\"690\" height=\"338\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.16.53</span><span class=\"informations\">767×376 19.1 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/d/1/d1c9ae41cbbfb3a00c13a0ffcb99ec3643ebf1f1.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.17.10\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/d/1/d1c9ae41cbbfb3a00c13a0ffcb99ec3643ebf1f1_2_690x388.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.17.10\" width=\"690\" height=\"388\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.17.10</span><span class=\"informations\">767×432 31.2 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/2/020f9add6dbeb1f00cb34231fd6ef2724e9b9f30.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.17.18\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/2/020f9add6dbeb1f00cb34231fd6ef2724e9b9f30_2_690x450.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.17.18\" width=\"690\" height=\"450\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.17.18</span><span class=\"informations\">791×517 44.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/0/007ec3d40e126c2c1936ceefc15649a2caa22646.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.17.42\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/0/007ec3d40e126c2c1936ceefc15649a2caa22646_2_690x273.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.17.42\" width=\"690\" height=\"273\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.17.42</span><span class=\"informations\">1553×616 107 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>, and I can’t wait to see its growth!</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/3/5/35c33b371e4c9b03853c2ae4918618c022c93c5b.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.11.51\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/3/5/35c33b371e4c9b03853c2ae4918618c022c93c5b_2_690x290.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.11.51\" width=\"690\" height=\"290\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.11.51</span><span class=\"informations\">1600×674 98.3 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/6/5/65616431bd5d597475954e072616138b02acd9ef.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.14.51\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/6/5/65616431bd5d597475954e072616138b02acd9ef_2_690x483.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.14.51\" width=\"690\" height=\"483\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.14.51</span><span class=\"informations\">777×545 39.8 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/2/3/23ce1347ebf42ec2c92620a2093fd43c90b4dac8.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.13.26\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/2/3/23ce1347ebf42ec2c92620a2093fd43c90b4dac8_2_614x500.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.13.26\" width=\"614\" height=\"500\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.13.26</span><span class=\"informations\">796×648 46.7 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/c/f/cf43a307a1e0f22850f891846965ec885c4eebac.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.12.54\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/c/f/cf43a307a1e0f22850f891846965ec885c4eebac_2_690x394.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.12.54\" width=\"690\" height=\"394\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.12.54</span><span class=\"informations\">874×500 36.5 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/1/c/1cde2a50a591820bb9e3629da1b8d10a2b9ec480.png\" title=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.12.48\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/1/c/1cde2a50a591820bb9e3629da1b8d10a2b9ec480_2_690x375.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.12.48\" width=\"690\" height=\"375\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screenshot 2025-09-07 at 15.12.48</span><span class=\"informations\">871×474 38.3 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>"
