      "author": "JoseDaher (Jose Daher)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Nice!</p>\n<p>I’ve tested it and managed to run a Sales Pipeline Plot as intended. It took me several tries, but it’s now deployed for account usage. I’m happy with its understanding of my prompts and its ability to suggest and implement pagination—otherwise, the plot would be useless.</p>\n<p>However, it’s still unclear to me whether I’ll be able to use it after the trial period.</p>\n<p>Best regards,</p>"
